column2: MAYBANK KIM ENG SECURITIES PTE. LTD.
BASED ON THE INFORMATION AVAILABLE TO THE TRUSTEE-MANAGER AS AT 12 MARCH 2019, 88.98% OF THE ISSUED ORDINARY UNITS OF THE TRUST
ARE HELD BY THE PUBLIC AND, THEREFORE RULE 723 OF THE LISTING MANUAL IS COMPLIED WITH.
THE TRUST DOES NOT HAVE ANY TREASURY UNITS OR CONVERTIBLE SECURITIES.
